subject: World Cup 2014 (Soccer)
Soccer
lead_paragraph: Japan became the first team to qualify for the 2014 World Cup, tying Australia, 1-1, on Keisuke Honda’s penalty kick in the first minute of second-half stoppage time in Saitama, Japan.
